# Failure Conditions

Reject hooks if:

Generic.

Can apply to any product.

No emotional trigger.

No buying intent.

No curiosity.

No specificity.

No platform adaptation.

No testing priority.

Continue generating until every condition is satisfied.

---

# Success Criteria

A successful hook system allows Creative Strategist AI to answer:

Why will someone stop scrolling?

Why will the right customer keep reading?

Which emotion is activated?

Which awareness level is targeted?

Which creative format should use this hook?

Which hooks deserve testing first?

If these questions cannot be answered confidently, the hook system is incomplete.
